Performance Issues
8. Excessive Color Reloading
File: ColorLoader.qml  
Line: 50
Problem:
Timer {
    interval: 10  // 100 times per second!
    running: true
    repeat: true
    onTriggered: {
        root.loadColors();
    }
}
- Reads and parses JSON file 100 times per second
- Causes unnecessary CPU usage
- May cause UI stuttering
Fix:
// Option 1: Use FileWatcher (recommended)
import Quickshell.Io
FileWatcher {
    path: root.colorsJsonFilePath
    onFileChanged: {
        root.loadColors();
    }
}
// Option 2: Increase interval significantly
Timer {
    interval: 5000  // 5 seconds
    running: true
    repeat: true
    onTriggered: {
        root.loadColors();
    }
}
Priority: HIGH
