9. Multiple Redundant Timers
Files: Multiple
Problem:
- Multiple timers polling the same data
- Battery.qml: 5-second timer (lines 612-621)
- Battery.qml: 10-second timer for GPU (lines 624-632)
- Battery.qml: 10-second timer for refresh rate (lines 635-642)
Fix:
Consolidate into a single timer with staggered updates:
Timer {
    interval: 5000
    running: true
    repeat: true
    onTriggered: {
        batteryProc.running = true;
        chargingProc.running = true;
        if (root.hasGpu && counter % 2 === 0) {
            getGpuMode.running = true;
        }
        getRefreshRate.running = true;
        counter++;
    }
}
property int counter: 0
